ed="T" n="0808a06"/><persName key="A011561">釋丹甫</persName>者，不知何許人也。性多警達，言必<lb
ed="T" n="0808a07"/>剛直，講授<anchor xml:id="beg0808sgsz1"/>唯<anchor xml:id="end0808sgsz1"/>勤，執持雅正。<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>風土，律範淵<lb
ed="T" n="0808a08"/>府<ptr type="glossary" target="#g688"/>也。<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>之唱導，從之者若玄金<ptr type="glossary" target="#g811"/>之就礠石<lb
ed="T" n="0808a09"/>焉。本習業於<persName key="A011564">亘文<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>法集，<persName key="A011564">文</persName>即<persName key="A011073">省躬</persName>之<persName key="A021880">游</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0808a10"/><persName key="A010088">夏</persName>也<ptr target="#n797"/>，<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>即<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>之嗣孫。順正命章<ptr type="glossary" target="#g13"/>，斡通祕賾<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g331"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0808a11"/>越自<persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>、<persName key="A010815">玄儼</persName>之後，罕能追躡，<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>之聲塵<lb
ed="T" n="0808a12"/>邁于前烈。然爾時<persName key="A011632">允文</persName>匠手，<placeName key="PL000000024082">相部</placeName><ptr target="#n3250"/>風行，<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>介<lb
ed="T" n="0808a13"/>于大律之間，行事之時，草從風偃焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0870-06-20" key="j20389922040147" notAfter-iso="+0873-08-18"><name>咸通</name>末</date><lb
ed="T" n="0808a14"/>出門生<persName key="A011562">智章</persName>等傳講，今亦法嗣存焉。或聞<lb
ed="T" n="0808a15"/>著《手記》<ptr target="#n1859"/>，尋且未獲，吁！惜哉！</p>
